{"tid":1625032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家仲記唔記得 「兄弟爬山  各自努力」  呢句說話","createTime":"2019-10-05T05:40:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T09:18:31.000Z","uid":204163,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d6a129ff91ef4dc8452c34473b0176b3a0175bb2","tid":1625032,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:40:27.000Z","msg":"我唔知大家點理解[兄弟爬山 各自努力]呢句意思<br />\n<br />\n我既理解既 雖然各有各做 但係同一目標有共識既, 而唔係一句[[我理解/核爆都唔割]]就得。<br />\n<br />\n前線勇武搞裝修既，黨鐵(包括旗下商場）同政府機構就隨時都<span style=\"color: red;\">無問題</span>；銀行中移動個類最多可以膠水塞大門, 幫手足放假又唔會太差形象，至少提款機可以拎到錢，重點係唔好俾人有咁多話柄。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食肆我地可以集中火力清算某幾間，例如美心皇宮+元氣; <br />\n1.有威嚇性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.休養生息抖下留下力;魔法師好辛苦，前線勇武少一個就真係少好多，我地唔好再送頭啦好無?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.外國記者/文宣手足有機會落墨同外界解釋點解我地會揀呢啲鋪嚟搞, 先會有人認同兼支持我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同行手足理解，但其他人無義務去理解, 千祈唔好辜負攬炒巴同各國前線記者既努力。<br />\n美國人權法可唔可以成功，輿論一定有影響;仲有英國，佢哋對殖民地一定有啲情意結，所以爭取佢哋嘅民意都好重要。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但重重重重重重點！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前線武勇主要快閃 完咗即走 唔好戀戰唔洗撚狗, 戀戰同勇住去撚狗係送頭行為；和理非會幫你地撚（太古城個晚就係好好既例子）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而和理非就集中文宣, weekend日頭就和平帶口罩(空氣差/有疑似伊波拉個案)咁行下街, 去下藍店（設計下文宣，上下twitter etc.)嘆冷氣，去懲罰下黃色小店；得閒啲就打去book下枱食飯（記得order少少中上價菜；有AE白金卡既巴絲更要識玩，訂10次出現2次仲要唔知幾時係真）。<br />\n逢夜晚就出嚟食糖水(記得帶口罩,空氣差又有疑似伊波拉), 又可以cover下前線。<br />\n就算有狗，我地都唔洗跑。我地咩都無做，佢叫散我地就慢慢散; 佢要捉就捉曬我地咁多個;就算不肯食彈，我地都係佔領道德高地; 即至佢捉，佢都charge唔到我地啲咩，我地甚至仲可以反咬佢濫捕。<br />\n<br />\n全民皆兵 唔係指個個都要做衝衝子，係我地有同一個敵人同一個理念。我地可以係哨兵同前線講邊到有狗嚟緊/點走最有效；我地可以係補給兵，提供唔同材料。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢個先係兄弟爬山既真正含意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請記住 和理非係勇武最強大既back up, 攰既時候可以休息下, 放心交俾和理非。<br />\n休息一日唔係怯唔係認同，我地口罩出街已經係反緊惡法！<br />\n煲底相見之前， 不離不棄！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n香港人 反抗"},{"pid":"1d66b0679dd05c9546a5e56bb12b36bc93a1bb76","tid":1625032,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:41:39.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"38042709cf01c93d639c13a5bd196460958f5ba4","tid":1625032,"uid":321913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:42:00.000Z","msg":"［裝修指南］維港沿岸篇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624936</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"283622b3c7f3ec87e020fba26e62a7f1aa7919d8","tid":1625032,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:44:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"145d2dd5b203a93f1471fc0772cea3c81b657418","tid":1625032,"uid":34140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:49:59.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山，各自努力"},{"pid":"a0b9e43ac0791d48ccf13643a2d42de959578fef","tid":1625032,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:54:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27322507aff66e658609562ea9254132c6cbae21","tid":1625032,"uid":257293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:54:40.000Z","msg":"其實裝修有好多種<br />\n點解唔裝修成連儂牆？<br />\n新聞出嘅圖可以贏到輿論同國際支持<br />\n又可以target警世呢啲紅底中資<br />\n佢哋要拆要清都要搞到一大輪<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/24852222_1729358367084760_1911336044043144089_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQkIOjsel3Yjc1B7cRnhIfagIvmR4f4aVTBnzK5PhcCs6SwzlwstlaxQaqELvb708RI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=6ff3cb4718a8dad53be9276dd33cad72&amp;oe=5E364A79\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F24852222_1729358367084760_1911336044043144089_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQkIOjsel3Yjc1B7cRnhIfagIvmR4f4aVTBnzK5PhcCs6SwzlwstlaxQaqELvb708RI%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D6ff3cb4718a8dad53be9276dd33cad72%26oe%3D5E364A79&h=7003ea3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝修 + 文宣 可以同時做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624381</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"955c453b8d131413878e8c158a7dd5a3e8b5433c","tid":1625032,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:21:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6d51e53f5a908c94f1245d48d5cb1425c49c0d3","tid":1625032,"uid":268854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:31:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7683cb24819e9d9edb2a6f4aa4d31f2b9bae36c","tid":1625032,"uid":12791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:29:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5edf7cc015118c98788adaa314353f06ac61cafe","tid":1625032,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:49:09.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"e5a15e0f81abb3e4f1ddb8ba1f9835fb86fe290a","tid":1625032,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:15:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ced3a2492770e3d304a8ca44fd747fab73646f0","tid":1625032,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:58:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"018857742d40115d26ff04e53453a1eed1d943ca","tid":1625032,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:58:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b8a471941a293cc87c355f37b2948bdaf44be12","tid":1625032,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:18:31.000Z","msg":"推"}]}